{
  "video_id": "N0vRIqeoefs",
  "title": "Why women should tell the stories of humanity | Jude Kelly",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12519.0,
      "end_time": 14399.0,
      "text": "Why do we think"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14423.0,
      "end_time": 19714.0,
      "text": "that stories by men are deemed to be of universal importance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19738.0,
      "end_time": 24593.0,
      "text": "and stories by women are thought to be merely about women?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26633.0,
      "end_time": 29372.0,
      "text": "My grandmother left school when she was 12."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29396.0,
      "end_time": 31670.0,
      "text": "She had 14 children."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32176.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34670.0,
      "text": "My mother left school when she was 15."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34910.0,
      "end_time": 35492.0,
      "text": "She was a secretary."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35516.0,
      "end_time": 39274.0,
      "text": "I graduated from university to become a theater director,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39298.0,
      "end_time": 43457.0,
      "text": "and that progress is entirely to do with the fact that people I&#39;ll never meet"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43481.0,
      "end_time": 45729.0,
      "text": "fought for women to have rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45753.0,
      "end_time": 48894.0,
      "text": "get the vote, get education, have progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48918.0,
      "end_time": 52503.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m determined to do the same, and obviously you are, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52527.0,
      "end_time": 53704.0,
      "text": "Why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53728.0,
      "end_time": 55285.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55309.0,
      "end_time": 59210.0,
      "text": "So I started a festival called WOW, Women of the World, seven years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59450.0,
      "end_time": 62490.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s now in 20 countries across five continents."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62730.0,
      "end_time": 65424.0,
      "text": "And one of those countries is Somaliland in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65447.0,
      "end_time": 67663.0,
      "text": "So I traveled there last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67687.0,
      "end_time": 73280.0,
      "text": "and part of the joy I had in going there was going to these caves."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74542.0,
      "end_time": 76718.0,
      "text": "The Laas Geel caves."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76742.0,
      "end_time": 82256.0,
      "text": "Now, these caves contain some of the oldest cave paintings in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82819.0,
      "end_time": 88940.0,
      "text": "These paintings are thought to be round about 9,000 to 11,000 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88930.0,
      "end_time": 90359.0,
      "text": "Art:"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90383.0,
      "end_time": 94146.0,
      "text": "what humanity has done ever since it evolved."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 94170.0,
      "end_time": 96293.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s how we speak about ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96317.0,
      "end_time": 98253.0,
      "text": "how we understand our identity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 98278.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "how we look at our surroundings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100500.0,
      "end_time": 103121.0,
      "text": "who we find out about each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103145.0,
      "end_time": 105354.0,
      "text": "because of the meaning of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105379.0,
      "end_time": 106703.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what art is for."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 107791.0,
      "end_time": 109753.0,
      "text": "So look at this little picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109777.0,
      "end_time": 111723.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s a little girl."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111747.0,
      "end_time": 114523.0,
      "text": "I thought it was a bit like me when I was a little girl."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115150.0,
      "end_time": 119182.0,
      "text": "And I thought, well, who painted this joyful, youthful figure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 119206.0,
      "end_time": 121310.0,
      "text": "And I asked the curator of the caves."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121334.0,
      "end_time": 124852.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Tell me about the men and women who painted these.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124876.0,
      "end_time": 128353.0,
      "text": "And he looked at me absolutely askance, and he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128377.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130589.00000000001,
      "text": "\"Women didn&#39;t paint these pictures.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131610.0,
      "end_time": 133565.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Well, it was 11,000 years ago.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133589.0,
      "end_time": 135480.0,
      "text": "I said, \"How do you know?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135720.0,
      "end_time": 137599.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137623.0,
      "end_time": 141353.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"Women don&#39;t do these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141378.0,
      "end_time": 145170.0,
      "text": "Men made these marks. Women don&#39;t.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146367.0,
      "end_time": 150137.0,
      "text": "Now, I wasn&#39;t really surprised,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150161.0,
      "end_time": 154219.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s an attitude that I&#39;ve seen continuously"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154243.0,
      "end_time": 157150.0,
      "text": "all my life as a theater maker."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158372.0,
      "end_time": 164182.0,
      "text": "We are told that divine knowledge comes down through the masculine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 164206.0,
      "end_time": 168792.0,
      "text": "whether it be to the imam, the priest, the rabbi, the holy man."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 169241.0,
      "end_time": 174537.0,
      "text": "Similarly, we&#39;re told that creative genius resides in the masculine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174561.0,
      "end_time": 176307.0,
      "text": "that it is the masculine"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176331.0,
      "end_time": 179396.0,
      "text": "that will be able to tell us about who we really are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 179420.0,
      "end_time": 182487.0,
      "text": "that the masculine will tell the universal story"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182511.0,
      "end_time": 184398.0,
      "text": "on behalf of all of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 184422.0,
      "end_time": 188997.0,
      "text": "whereas women artists will really just talk about women&#39;s experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189210.0,
      "end_time": 192397.0,
      "text": "women&#39;s issues only really relevant to women"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 192421.0,
      "end_time": 195399.0,
      "text": "and of passing interest to men --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 195423.0,
      "end_time": 197325.0,
      "text": "and really only some men."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 197729.0,
      "end_time": 200000.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s that conviction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200240.0,
      "end_time": 201405.0,
      "text": "that that we are taught,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201429.0,
      "end_time": 205229.0,
      "text": "that I think colors so much of whether we&#39;re prepared to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 205253.0,
      "end_time": 207754.0,
      "text": "that women&#39;s stories really matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207778.0,
      "end_time": 211325.0,
      "text": "And unless we&#39;re prepared to believe that women&#39;s stories really matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211349.0,
      "end_time": 214339.0,
      "text": "then women&#39;s rights don&#39;t really matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 214363.0,
      "end_time": 217350.0,
      "text": "and then change can&#39;t really come."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 218696.0,
      "end_time": 223406.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you about two examples of stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223430.0,
      "end_time": 226368.0,
      "text": "that are thought to be of universal importance:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226392.0,
      "end_time": 229148.0,
      "text": "\"E.T.\" and \"Hamlet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 229172.0,
      "end_time": 232283.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232307.0,
      "end_time": 235572.0,
      "text": "So I took my two children when they were little --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235597.0,
      "end_time": 238847.0,
      "text": "Caroline was eight and Robby was five --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238871.0,
      "end_time": 240438.0,
      "text": "to see \"E.T.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 240462.0,
      "end_time": 243846.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a fantastic story of this little alien"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 243871.0,
      "end_time": 245822.0,
      "text": "who ends up in an American family"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 245846.0,
      "end_time": 249550.0,
      "text": "with a mum, two brothers and a sister,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 249790.0,
      "end_time": 250722.0,
      "text": "but he wants to go home."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 251540.0,
      "end_time": 254160.0,
      "text": "Not only that, but some really bad scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 254184.0,
      "end_time": 256558.0,
      "text": "want to do some experiments on him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 256582.0,
      "end_time": 258267.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re looking for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 258813.0,
      "end_time": 260868.0,
      "text": "So the children have a plot."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 260892.0,
      "end_time": 263729.0,
      "text": "They decide they&#39;re going to take him back to his spaceship"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 263754.0,
      "end_time": 264905.0,
      "text": "as soon as they can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 264929.0,
      "end_time": 266803.0,
      "text": "and they plop him in a bicycle basket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 266827.0,
      "end_time": 268169.0,
      "text": "and off they ride."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 268193.0,
      "end_time": 272890.0,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the baddies have found out, and they&#39;re catching up"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 272113.0,
      "end_time": 274470.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve got sirens and they&#39;ve got their guns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 274494.0,
      "end_time": 277168.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve got the loud-hailers, it&#39;s terribly frightening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277192.0,
      "end_time": 279112.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re closing up on the children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 279136.0,
      "end_time": 281232.0,
      "text": "and the children are never going to make it."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 281256.0,
      "end_time": 285349.0,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, magically, the bikes fly up in the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285373.0,
      "end_time": 286912.0,
      "text": "over the clouds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 286936.0,
      "end_time": 288123.0,
      "text": "over the moon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 288148.0,
      "end_time": 290439.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re going to save \"E.T.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 291214.0,
      "end_time": 293492.0,
      "text": "So I turn to see my children&#39;s faces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 293516.0,
      "end_time": 297986.0,
      "text": "and Robby is enraptured, he&#39;s there with them, he&#39;s saving E.T.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 298100.0,
      "end_time": 299866.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s a happy boy."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 299890.0,
      "end_time": 303270.0,
      "text": "And I turn to Caroline, and she&#39;s crying her eyes out."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 303686.0,
      "end_time": 305231.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"What&#39;s the matter?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 305255.0,
      "end_time": 310790.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"Why can&#39;t I save E.T.? Why can&#39;t I come?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 311242.0,
      "end_time": 313601.0,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden I realized:"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 313625.0,
      "end_time": 315360.0,
      "text": "they weren&#39;t children;"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 315677.0,
      "end_time": 316940.0,
      "text": "they were boys --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 317575.0,
      "end_time": 319640.0,
      "text": "all boys."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 319664.0,
      "end_time": 322640.0,
      "text": "And Caroline, who had invested so much in E.T.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 322665.0,
      "end_time": 324835.0,
      "text": "well, she wasn&#39;t invited to save him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 324859.0,
      "end_time": 327536.0,
      "text": "and she felt humiliated and spurned."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 328232.0,
      "end_time": 329981.0,
      "text": "So I wrote to Steven Spielberg --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 330500.0,
      "end_time": 336173.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 336197.0,
      "end_time": 338747.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"I don&#39;t know if you understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 338771.0,
      "end_time": 341150.0,
      "text": "the psychological importance of what&#39;s happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 341174.0,
      "end_time": 343674.0,
      "text": "and are you prepared to pay for the therapy bills?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 343698.0,
      "end_time": 345111.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 345136.0,
      "end_time": 348108.0,
      "text": "Twenty years later, I haven&#39;t had a word back from him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 348132.0,
      "end_time": 349570.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m still hopeful."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349594.0,
      "end_time": 351204.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 351228.0,
      "end_time": 352832.0,
      "text": "But I thought it was interesting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 352856.0,
      "end_time": 355728.0,
      "text": "because if you read reviews of what he intended with E.T.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 355752.0,
      "end_time": 357543.0,
      "text": "he says very specifically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 357567.0,
      "end_time": 360690.0,
      "text": "\"I wanted the world to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 360930.0,
      "end_time": 363300.0,
      "text": "that we should love and embrace difference.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 363324.0,
      "end_time": 367946.0,
      "text": "But somehow he didn&#39;t include the idea of girls&#39; difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 367970.0,
      "end_time": 369662.0,
      "text": "in this thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 369686.0,
      "end_time": 373996.0,
      "text": "He thought he was writing a story about all humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 374200.0,
      "end_time": 376970.0,
      "text": "Caroline thought he was marginalizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 376122.0,
      "end_time": 377551.0,
      "text": "half of humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 377575.0,
      "end_time": 380659.0,
      "text": "He thought he was writing a story about human goodness;"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 380683.0,
      "end_time": 385690.0,
      "text": "she thought he was writing a lad&#39;s heroic adventure."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 385848.0,
      "end_time": 387609.0,
      "text": "And this is common."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 388332.0,
      "end_time": 393453.0,
      "text": "Men feel they have been given the mantle for universal communication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 393477.0,
      "end_time": 395429.0,
      "text": "but of course, how could they be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 395453.0,
      "end_time": 399532.0,
      "text": "They are writing from male experience through male&#39;s eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 401851.0,
      "end_time": 404690.0,
      "text": "We have to have a look at this ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 404930.0,
      "end_time": 407769.0,
      "text": "We have to be prepared to go back through all our books and our films,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 407793.0,
      "end_time": 409130.0,
      "text": "all our favorite things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 409154.0,
      "end_time": 411984.0,
      "text": "and say, \"Actually, this is written by a male artist --"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 412800.0,
      "end_time": 413996.0,
      "text": "not an artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 414200.0,
      "end_time": 416424.0,
      "text": "We have to see that so many of these stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 416448.0,
      "end_time": 418584.0,
      "text": "are written through a male perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 418608.0,
      "end_time": 420545.0,
      "text": "Which is fine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 420569.0,
      "end_time": 424670.0,
      "text": "but then females need to have 50 percent of the rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 424910.0,
      "end_time": 426645.0,
      "text": "for the stage, the film, the novel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 426669.0,
      "end_time": 428457.0,
      "text": "the place of creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 429381.0,
      "end_time": 431179.0,
      "text": "Let me talk about \"Hamlet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 431204.0,
      "end_time": 432897.0,
      "text": "To be or not to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 432921.0,
      "end_time": 434135.0,
      "text": "That is the question."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 434818.0,
      "end_time": 436820.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not my question."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 436607.0,
      "end_time": 440356.0,
      "text": "My question is: Why was I taught as a young woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 440380.0,
      "end_time": 444737.0,
      "text": "that this was the quintessential example of human dilemma"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 444761.0,
      "end_time": 446457.0,
      "text": "and human experience?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 446481.0,
      "end_time": 447817.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a marvelous story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 447841.0,
      "end_time": 453177.0,
      "text": "but actually, it&#39;s about a young man fearful that he won&#39;t be able to make it"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 453201.0,
      "end_time": 455866.0,
      "text": "as a powerful figure in a male world"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 455890.0,
      "end_time": 458604.0,
      "text": "unless he takes revenge for his father&#39;s murder."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 459372.0,
      "end_time": 464500.0,
      "text": "He talks a great deal to us about suicide being an option,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 464740.0,
      "end_time": 468743.0,
      "text": "but the reality is that the person who actually commits suicide, Ophelia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 468767.0,
      "end_time": 471265.0,
      "text": "after she&#39;s been humiliated and abused by him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 471289.0,
      "end_time": 474465.0,
      "text": "never gets a chance to talk to the audience about her feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 474489.0,
      "end_time": 477431.0,
      "text": "And then when he&#39;s finished with Ophelia, he turns on his mum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 477455.0,
      "end_time": 480753.0,
      "text": "because basically she has the audacity to fall in love with his uncle"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 480778.0,
      "end_time": 481990.0,
      "text": "and enjoy sex."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 482140.0,
      "end_time": 484510.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 484750.0,
      "end_time": 486163.0,
      "text": "It is a great story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 486187.0,
      "end_time": 491258.0,
      "text": "but it is a story about male conflict, male dilemma, male struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 491957.0,
      "end_time": 496149.0,
      "text": "But I was told this was the story of human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 496173.0,
      "end_time": 499216.0,
      "text": "despite the fact that it only had two women in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 499240.0,
      "end_time": 501801.0,
      "text": "And unless I reeducate myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 501825.0,
      "end_time": 503550.0,
      "text": "I am always going to think"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 503574.0,
      "end_time": 507315.0,
      "text": "that women&#39;s stories matter less than men&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 507986.0,
      "end_time": 509721.0,
      "text": "A woman could have written \"Hamlet,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 509745.0,
      "end_time": 511832.0,
      "text": "but she would have written it differently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 511856.0,
      "end_time": 514463.0,
      "text": "and it wouldn&#39;t have had global recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 514488.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516559.00000000006,
      "text": "As the writer Margaret Atwood says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 516582.0,
      "end_time": 519680.0,
      "text": "\"When a man writes about doing the dishes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 519919.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520386.99999999994,
      "text": "it&#39;s realism."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 521198.0,
      "end_time": 523319.0,
      "text": "When a woman writes about doing it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 523344.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525859.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s an unfortunate genetic disposition.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 525883.0,
      "end_time": 527920.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 527116.0,
      "end_time": 530949.0,
      "text": "Now, this is not just something that belongs to then."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 530974.0,
      "end_time": 532774.0,
      "text": "I mean, when I was a young girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 532798.0,
      "end_time": 535422.0,
      "text": "wanting desperately to be a theater director,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 535446.0,
      "end_time": 538285.0,
      "text": "this is what my male lecturer said to me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 538309.0,
      "end_time": 542381.0,
      "text": "\"Well, there are three women directors in Britain,\" he said, \"Jude.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 542405.0,
      "end_time": 546512.0,
      "text": "\"There&#39;s Joan Knight, who&#39;s a lesbian, there&#39;s Joan Littlewood, who&#39;s retired,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 546536.0,
      "end_time": 549315.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s Buzz Goodbody, who&#39;s just killed herself."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 549340.0,
      "end_time": 551596.0,
      "text": "So, which of those three would you like to be?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 551620.0,
      "end_time": 552673.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 552697.0,
      "end_time": 557283.0,
      "text": "Now, leaving aside the disgusting slur on gay women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 557307.0,
      "end_time": 560152.0,
      "text": "the fact is, he wanted to humiliate me."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 560176.0,
      "end_time": 563935.0,
      "text": "He thought it was silly that I wanted to be a director."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 563959.0,
      "end_time": 566930.0,
      "text": "And I told my friend Marin Alsop, the conductor, and she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 566954.0,
      "end_time": 569703.0,
      "text": "\"Oh yes, well, my music teacher said exactly the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 569727.0,
      "end_time": 571896.0,
      "text": "He said, &#39;Women don&#39;t conduct.&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 572524.0,
      "end_time": 575247.0,
      "text": "But all these years later, we&#39;ve made our mark."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 575271.0,
      "end_time": 577501.0,
      "text": "You think, \"Well, it&#39;ll be different now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 577525.0,
      "end_time": 580190.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m afraid it&#39;s not different now."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 580430.0,
      "end_time": 583488.0,
      "text": "The current head of the Paris Conservatoire"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 583512.0,
      "end_time": 586939.0,
      "text": "said recently, \"It takes great physical strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 586963.0,
      "end_time": 588444.0,
      "text": "to conduct a symphony,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 588468.0,
      "end_time": 589919.0,
      "text": "and women are too weak.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 589943.0,
      "end_time": 591396.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 591420.0,
      "end_time": 593358.0,
      "text": "The artist George Baselitz said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 593383.0,
      "end_time": 595670.0,
      "text": "\"Well, the fact is women can&#39;t paint."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 595694.0,
      "end_time": 597540.0,
      "text": "Well -- they can&#39;t paint very well.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 598140.0,
      "end_time": 600402.0,
      "text": "The writer V.S. Naipaul said two years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 600426.0,
      "end_time": 604180.0,
      "text": "\"I can read two paragraphs and know immediately if it&#39;s written by a woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 604420.0,
      "end_time": 606743.0,
      "text": "and I just stop reading, because it&#39;s not worthy of me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 606767.0,
      "end_time": 608440.0,
      "text": "Audience: Whoa!"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 609209.0,
      "end_time": 610842.0,
      "text": "And it goes on."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 612817.0,
      "end_time": 614805.0,
      "text": "We have to find a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 614829.0,
      "end_time": 617473.0,
      "text": "of stopping young girls and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 617497.0,
      "end_time": 620338.0,
      "text": "feeling not only that their story doesn&#39;t matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 620362.0,
      "end_time": 623572.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re not allowed to be the storyteller."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 624481.0,
      "end_time": 628640.0,
      "text": "Because once you feel that you can&#39;t stand in the central space"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 628880.0,
      "end_time": 631960.0,
      "text": "and speak on behalf of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 631120.0,
      "end_time": 636195.0,
      "text": "you will feel that you can offer your goods up to a small, select group."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 636219.0,
      "end_time": 639735.0,
      "text": "You will tend to do smaller work on smaller stages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 639759.0,
      "end_time": 641792.0,
      "text": "your economic power will be less,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 641816.0,
      "end_time": 644288.0,
      "text": "your reach of audiences will be less,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 644312.0,
      "end_time": 648653.0,
      "text": "and your credit will be less as an artist."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 649377.0,
      "end_time": 654632.0,
      "text": "And we do finally give artists these incredible, prominent spaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 654656.0,
      "end_time": 655819.0,
      "text": "in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 655844.0,
      "end_time": 657583.0,
      "text": "because they are our storytellers."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 657607.0,
      "end_time": 660736.0,
      "text": "Now, why should it matter to you if you&#39;re not an artist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 660760.0,
      "end_time": 664500.0,
      "text": "Supposing you&#39;re an accountant or an entrepreneur or a medic"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 664290.0,
      "end_time": 665196.0,
      "text": "or a scientist:"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 665220.0,
      "end_time": 667822.0,
      "text": "Should you care about women artists?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 667846.0,
      "end_time": 669902.0,
      "text": "Absolutely, you must,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 669926.0,
      "end_time": 673338.0,
      "text": "because as you can see from the cave paintings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 673362.0,
      "end_time": 675430.0,
      "text": "all civilizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 675670.0,
      "end_time": 677271.0,
      "text": "all of humanity"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 677925.0,
      "end_time": 681881.0,
      "text": "have relied upon artists to tell the human story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 681905.0,
      "end_time": 685174.0,
      "text": "and if the human story is finally told by men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 685198.0,
      "end_time": 686934.0,
      "text": "take my word for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 686958.0,
      "end_time": 688675.0,
      "text": "it will be about men."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 689491.0,
      "end_time": 692175.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s make a change."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 692199.0,
      "end_time": 694401.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s make a change to all our institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 694425.0,
      "end_time": 695699.0,
      "text": "and not just in the West."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 695724.0,
      "end_time": 700143.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t forget -- this message of incapability of women"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 700167.0,
      "end_time": 702192.0,
      "text": "to hold creative genius"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 702216.0,
      "end_time": 707130.0,
      "text": "is being told to girls and women in Nigeria, in China, in Russia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 707154.0,
      "end_time": 708317.0,
      "text": "in Indonesia."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 708341.0,
      "end_time": 711500.0,
      "text": "All over the world, girls and women are being told"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 711740.0,
      "end_time": 715991.0,
      "text": "that they can&#39;t finally hold the idea of creative inspiration."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 716951.0,
      "end_time": 718600.0,
      "text": "And I want to ask you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 718624.0,
      "end_time": 720338.0,
      "text": "Do you believe that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 720362.0,
      "end_time": 724156.0,
      "text": "Do you believe that women can be a creative genius?"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 724988.0,
      "end_time": 730727.0,
      "text": "(Applause and cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 730751.0,
      "end_time": 732411.0,
      "text": "Well then, please go forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 732436.0,
      "end_time": 734686.0,
      "text": "support women artists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 734710.0,
      "end_time": 736184.0,
      "text": "buy their work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 736208.0,
      "end_time": 738476.0,
      "text": "insist that their voices are heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 738500.0,
      "end_time": 741770.0,
      "text": "find platforms on which their voices will be made."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 742500.0,
      "end_time": 744287.0,
      "text": "And remember this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 744311.0,
      "end_time": 747590.0,
      "text": "that in a sense, if we&#39;re going to get past this moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 747614.0,
      "end_time": 751466.0,
      "text": "of a world where we know that we are unequal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 751490.0,
      "end_time": 754687.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s artists who have to imagine a different world."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 754711.0,
      "end_time": 758321.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m calling on all artists, women and men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 758345.0,
      "end_time": 761685.0,
      "text": "to imagine a gender-equal world."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 762146.0,
      "end_time": 764329.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s paint it. Let&#39;s draw it."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 764353.0,
      "end_time": 766147.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s write about it. Let&#39;s film it."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 766172.0,
      "end_time": 768580.0,
      "text": "And if we could imagine it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 768820.0,
      "end_time": 771562.0,
      "text": "then we would have the energy and the stamina"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 771586.0,
      "end_time": 773750.0,
      "text": "to work towards it."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 773622.0,
      "end_time": 775675.0,
      "text": "When I see this little girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 775700.0,
      "end_time": 777740.0,
      "text": "11,000 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 777764.0,
      "end_time": 781225.0,
      "text": "I want to know that the little girl now"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 781249.0,
      "end_time": 784533.0,
      "text": "can stand there and think she&#39;s entitled to her dreams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 784557.0,
      "end_time": 786847.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s entitled to her destiny"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 786871.0,
